title: 3D World 119 CD ISO
description:
Welcome to the disc for 3D World 119. 

Autobot, Decepticon... or self-build?
To mark this issue's Transformers cover
feature, we asked LightWave 3D artist
Dan DeEntremont to show us how to rig
a transforming robot of our very own.
You can find it in the Tutorials area
of the disc, along with this issue's
other hands-on content.

But if you'd prefer not to create your
content entirely from scratch, the disc 
also contains figure models worth $233 
from aXYZ design, buildings worth $232 
from Flat Pyramid, a Poser figure pack, 
14 sound FX clips and 15 texture sets.

Let us know what you think by clicking 
Feedback in the menu. Enjoy the disc...
